Data licensing
--------------
Each source dataset in data/ retains its original license:

- FracTracker Alliance: see https://www.fractracker.org/ for terms.
- EPA AQS, USGS, Census ACS, FCC Form 477, DOE LEAD, CDC SVI: U.S. federal
  government works, generally public domain.
- NREL SLOPE, NREL ReV 2023: see https://maps.nrel.gov/slope/ and
  https://www.nrel.gov/ for terms.
- SEPA / NCCETC DELTa: Copyright (c) SEPA and N.C. Clean Energy Technology
  Center, 2025-2026. See https://sepapower.org/large-load-tariffs-database/.
- E3 (2026) source whitepaper: Copyright (c) Energy and Environmental
  Economics, Inc.

The author-built scoring rubric and merged analytic outputs in this
repository are released under the MIT license above.
